                </li></ul>
                </div><div id="s-lg-database-desc-9389656" class="s-lg-database-desc">Research on crime, its causes and impacts, legal and social implications, as well as litigation and crime trends. Includes  scholarly journals, correctional and law enforcement trade publications, crime reports, crime blogs and other materials.</div>
                    </div></li>
                        <li class="">
                        
                    <div id="s-lg-content-9389567" class=""><a href="https://ezproxy.lib.ryerson.ca/login?url=https://search.proquest.com/cbcacomplete"  target="_blank"  onclick="return springSpace.springTrack.trackLink({link: this,_st_type_id: '16',_st_content_id: '9389567'});">Canadian Business & Current Affairs Database (CBCA)</a> 
                <div class="s-lg-icons pad-left-sm"><ul>
                <li><img loading="lazy" alt="Has Canadian Content" class="s-lg-icon" src="//libapps-ca.s3.amazonaws.com/sites/2734/icons/7435/Canadian.png" title="Has Canadian Content &nbsp;"/>
                </li>
                <li><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/eresources/cbcomp/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" alt="More Info on Library Subscribed Resource" class="s-lg-icon" src="//libapps-ca.s3.amazonaws.com/sites/2734/icons/7444/LibGuides_Info3.png" title="More Info on Library Subscribed Resource &nbsp;"/> <span class="fa fa-fw fa-external-link" aria-hidden="true" title="This link opens in a new window"></span> <span class="sr-only">This link opens in a new window</span></a>
